  "detailed_description": "<h1>Special Offer</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⭐⭐⭐ <strong>This game is part of the Cozy & Emotional Stories bundle.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get the complete collection with a discount.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802790/extras/56d2b8827fcf410fdb6e1d86de0e0a99.avif?t=1772760954\" width=706 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802790/extras/20139649efba83c3113dd2759b9198e9.avif?t=1772760954\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>\"<strong>Why do you love me?</strong>\" - is a short kinetic novel in the \"<i>romance</i>\" genre. <br>Apparently it is about love and relationship. About the difficulties that come within and how to overcome them. <br>Players are given five stories. <br>We hope our gane will help players in their relationship including self-reflection. On Valentine's Day and just everyday. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802790/extras/3adbd6e37932aecf439c85ccaefc99c1.avif?t=1772760954\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Five unique sketches from our lives.<br></li><li>Graphics made with love.<br></li><li>A script made with heart.<br></li><li>Music made with money.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802790/extras/fa6869eaca32f374d27f62dd36ed08e2.avif?t=1772760954\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>The game was created by two developers, Pasha and Sasha, who want to take this opportunity to say hello to their moms and dads.",
